               <msContents>
                  <summary>An oath by a katasporeus stating that he has measured the entire plot of land sown. A list of the measured plots and what will be grown on them seems to follow (lines 16-22). As the katasporeus is also concerned with the sowing of land, one need not wonder that this task should be entrusted to him.</summary>
